window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Shanaya has just bagged a new job and she is on top of the world. </p> <p>The only thing missing in her life is a man. In a bid to celebrate, she doesn't want to waste a chance to have some fun. While looking for a date, she meets a mystery man on Tinder – someone who makes her knees go weak and makes her think naughty stuff. But all she wants is to have a good time. </p> <p>Will Shanaya just have a good time or will she let him take her to heights of unknown pleasure? Is he the man of her dreams, someone she had been waiting for all along? </p> <p>Join Shanaya in one crazy night of passion and fun as she says<i> Just Tinder Me Baby</i>.</p>"; 
